OL,5, Andrew "Freddie" Flintoff has reached a
OL,6, settlement with the BBC after he was   
OL,7, hurt in an accident while filming Top  
OL,8, Gear last year.                        
OL,10,FThe Sun reported that the deal with BBC
OL,11,FStudios is based on the ex-England     
OL,12,Fcricketer missing out on two years of  
OL,13,Fearnings - and worth #9m.              
OL,15,FFilming of the series was suspended    
OL,16,Fpending a review into the incident.    
OL,18,FThe payout will not be funded by the TV
OL,19,Flicence fee, as BBC Studios is a       
OL,20,Fcommercial arm of the broadcaster.     
